<template>
        div
        
</template>

<script>
import paintings from '../data/paintings.js'

export default {
    name:"PaintingView",
    data(){
        return {
            paintings: paintings,
            painting: {}
        }
    },
    created(){
        let paintingId = Number(this.$route.params.id);
        this.painting = this.paintings.find(painting=>painting.id == paintingId);
    }
}
</script>
